Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,換夏裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一大早就吃冰淇淋…
