Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,空…空氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,成為高中生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(359,655)\fs40}察言觀色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,「空氣」這種行為就不再僅僅是慣用句了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要實際操作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,花…小花名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 受教了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.23,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.51,0:22:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子很擅長讓貓親近自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.77,0:23:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,榮依子好厲害啊
