Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,小冠也超級黏榮依子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個 對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.21,0:23:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
